<a href="http://www.lochaber-guides.co.uk/" target="_blank">Dave</a> and I were working on a Climbing Wall Award Training with students from West Highland College's <a href="https://www.whc.uhi.ac.uk/studying-at-whc/school-of-adventure-studies" target="_blank">School of Adventure Studies</a>. On the first day we went to <a href="https://www.ice-factor.co.uk/" target="_blank">The Ice Factor</a> and on the second it was <a href="http://threewisemonkeysclimbing.com/" target="_blank">Three Wise Monkeys</a>. Its great to have 2 good walls so close to use now!<br />Earlier in the week I was down at <a href="http://www.theboardroomclimbing.com/" target="_blank">The Boardroom</a> as part of my role on the <a href="http://www.abcwalls.co.uk/" target="_blank">ABC</a> Training Committee where I also got a chance to try out the new <a href="http://www.wildcountry.com/revo/" target="_blank">Wild Country Revo</a> belay device.<br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-wACusUBuOws/WDDuVjvC-yI/AAAAAAAAXzE/eyWeua_06c8jiPU4qekPJgIMn6wqzt55gCLcB/s1600/P1000410.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="240" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-wACusUBuOws/WDDuVjvC-yI/AAAAAAAAXzE/eyWeua_06c8jiPU4qekPJgIMn6wqzt55gCLcB/s320/P1000410.JPG" width="320" /></a></div><div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;The Revo</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-CcWqJbcGUUI/WDDuVRy2tHI/AAAAAAAAXzA/a44CIvJI7DI9aXULx3yegGCZgCdkqZXUQCLcB/s1600/P1000413.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="320" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-CcWqJbcGUUI/WDDuVRy2tHI/AAAAAAAAXzA/a44CIvJI7DI9aXULx3yegGCZgCdkqZXUQCLcB/s320/P1000413.jpg" width="240" /></a></div><div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;Jimmy thinking about good practise in belaying</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: cen